enhanced_objects.name: lamp post
enhanced_objects.artistic_description: Tall metal structure glowing with warm amber light from within, casting soft halos through the dim indoor atmosphere. The painted surface shows subtle brushstrokes of rust-brown and deep charcoal, with light catching on the curved metal edges in impressionistic dabs of golden yellow. The glass housing reflects muted tones of the surrounding space in fragmented, dreamy patches.

enhanced_objects.name: toy
enhanced_objects.artistic_description: Small plastic figure rendered in soft patches of faded red and cream, its glossy surface catching scattered light in impressionistic highlights. The edges blur slightly in the subdued indoor lighting, with subtle shadows pooling around its base in cool gray tones. Tiny details dissolve into broader color fields when viewed from a distance.

enhanced_objects.name: sack
enhanced_objects.artistic_description: Rough burlap texture suggested through thick impasto strokes of warm brown and ochre, absorbing the soft ambient light rather than reflecting it. The fabric folds create deep shadows in burnt umber, while raised threads catch tiny glimmers of light in pale tan highlights. The matte surface drinks in the muted atmosphere.

enhanced_objects.name: pumpkin
enhanced_objects.artistic_description: Vibrant orange sphere rendered in thick dabs of cadmium orange and deep rust, its curved surface catching warm light in impressionistic patches. The matte rind shows subtle variations from pale pumpkin to burnt sienna, with soft shadows pooling in natural creases in deep umber. The stem appears as a dark olive-green dab against the glowing orange.

enhanced_objects.name: round table
enhanced_objects.artistic_description: Wooden surface painted in broad strokes of warm walnut brown and amber, with scattered highlights of soft cream where light pools across the smooth top. The legs appear as darker vertical strokes of deep umber and chocolate, with subtle reflections of the surrounding colors dancing across the polished wood in fragmented, dreamy patches.

enhanced_objects.name: orange
enhanced_objects.artistic_description: Small sphere of brilliant citrus color, its dimpled skin catching light in scattered dabs of bright tangerine and pale yellow. The matte surface shows subtle variations in saturation, with soft shadows creating depth in muted coral tones. Tiny highlights appear as impressionistic specks of pale cream against the vibrant orange field.

enhanced_objects.name: bread
enhanced_objects.artistic_description: Golden-brown loaf suggested through thick impasto strokes of warm ochre, pale wheat, and deep amber. The crusty surface shows textured peaks and valleys where light catches in bright creamy highlights, while shadowed crevices deepen to rich burnt sienna. The matte finish absorbs the soft ambient light, creating a gentle, inviting warmth.

enhanced_objects.name: canopy
enhanced_objects.artistic_description: Fabric overhead rendered in broad, loose strokes of muted burgundy and deep plum, its draped folds creating soft shadows in rich eggplant tones. The material catches scattered light in subtle highlights of dusty rose and mauve, while the overall surface appears velvety and matte, absorbing the subdued indoor atmosphere into its rich color field.

final_prompts.main_prompt: A Impressionism painting depicting a calm and relaxed evening scene with subdued, gentle atmosphere under mixed soft lighting. In the foreground, a large lamp post of warm amber and charcoal metal stands gently aged with subtle weathering, with a small toy in faded red and cream plastic placed next to it, appearing gently worn from play. In the midground, a medium round table of polished walnut brown and amber wood sits under a dominant canopy of gently draped and flowing burgundy and plum fabric. On the table's surface rests a medium pumpkin in fresh cadmium orange and rust, a small orange in unblemished tangerine and coral, and a medium loaf of bread in warm ochre and wheat tones, all appearing freshly baked and plump. Beside the table, a medium sack in slightly crumpled warm brown and ochre burlap leans softly against it. The entire composition captures the quiet harmony of objects in their spatial relationships with loose, visible brushstrokes and atmospheric perspective.
